          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Aged 15 years or over; - with HCM (non-valvular) defined by ultrasound with left ventricle thickness greater or equal to 13 mm (familial) or greater or equal to 15 mm (sporadic); - Patient was informed and gave their consent.  "
          },
